ttp.RequestTarget\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Http</span>.<span class=\"name\">RequestTarget</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"HTTP request target forms as defined in RFC 9112 Section 3.3.\n\nReference: https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc9112.html#section-3.3\n","docLink":"./Std/Internal/Http/Data/URI/Basic.html#Std.Http.RequestTarget","kind":"inductive","line":844,"name":"Std.Http.RequestTarget","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/3dc1a088b6d2d8eafe25a7cd7ec7b58d731bd7cc/src/Std/Internal/Http/Data/URI/Basic.lean#L844-L873"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Internal/Http/Data/URI/Basic.html#Std.Http.URI.normalize\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Http</span>.<span class=\"name\">URI</span>.<span class=\"name\">normalize</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">uri</span> : <a href=\"./Std/Internal/Http/Data/URI/Basic.html#Std.Http.URI\">URI</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Std/Internal/Http/Data/URI/Basic.html#Std.Http.URI\">URI</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Partially normalizes a URI by removing dot-segments from the path (`.` and `..`)\naccording to RFC 3986 Section 5.2.4.\n\nThis does not apply the full normalization set from RFC 3986 Section 6 — for example,\ncase normalization, percent-encoding normalization, and default-port normalization are\nnot performed.\n","docLink":"./Std/Internal/Http/Data/URI/Basic.html#Std.Http.URI.normalize","kind":"def","line":831,"name":"Std.Http.URI.normalize","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/3dc1a088b6d2d8eafe25a7cd7ec7b58d731bd7cc/src/Std/Internal/Http/Data/URI/Basic.lean#L831-L840"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_head